caption: #contest #contest Sorry once again I don't have any pictures of us together which brings a tear to my eye and I don't want it to be just of an album cover becuase you would never know what I look like if you know what I'm saying? but besides that I have told the same story over and over on ever other post and I'm tired of repeating all I really have to say is that I love you and you mean every thing to me and honestly I don't have to meet you to make my life better becuase you already have but it would just be amazing and honestly the best time of my life❤️ I love you guys so freaking much and I don't know how to show you all my love and support becuase there's just to much! #contest @jack&jackoffical
